Does this happen often
in Gangnam Police Station?

99
00:05:39,047 --> 00:05:40,465
No, sir.

100
00:05:40,548 --> 00:05:42,759
Absolutely not.

101
00:05:42,842 --> 00:05:44,427
Sir.

102
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:47,847
