654
00:50:39,202 --> 00:50:43,290
to change her mind.

655
00:50:43,915 --> 00:50:45,459
I promise

656
00:50:47,878 --> 00:50:49,463
I won't let you down, Boss.

657
00:50:53,759 --> 00:50:54,843
Okay.

658
00:50:57,637 --> 00:50:59,765
